comments.body:
like this cultivar https://www.picturethisai.com/en/wiki/Achillea_ptarmica__The_Pearl_.html

I'm not sure either, but they do seem very similar
You're right. It does look the same and it's quite different from the wild type! Thanks!
I'm not sure - there were 20-30 in an area of 1-2 m2. It doesn't look like Achillea ptarmica to me.

vermutlich ursprünglich aus Gartenhaltung, ich glaub nicht, dass gefüllte Blüten natürlich vorkommen?
